# Root-level safety net: never commit secrets anywhere in the repo
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.env_encoded
**/keys/
**/gcp_service_account*.json
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[oc]
**/.venv
**/venv/
**/env/

# Downloaded data
**/dataset/

# IDE and OS
.DS_Store
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Build and misc
**/build/
**/dist/
**/*.egg-info/
**/.terraform/
